<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NakamaStream - Mantenimiento</title>
    <meta name="description" content="NakamaStream se encuentra en mantenimiento. Volveremos pronto con novedades.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="NakamaStream - En Mantenimiento">
    <meta property="og:description" content="NakamaStream se encuentra en mantenimiento. Volveremos pronto con novedades.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://nakamastream.lat/">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="NakamaStream - En Mantenimiento">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="NakamaStream se encuentra en mantenimiento. Volveremos pronto con novedades.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'custom-red': '#ff6b6b',
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'float': 'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
                        'pulse-slow': 'pulse 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        float: {
                            '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
                            '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-20px)' },
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#121212] min-h-screen flex flex-col text-white">
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8">
        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
            <!-- Logo y Título -->
            <div class="relative">
                <img src="https://github.com/NakamaStream/Resources/raw/main/NakamStream-logo-HD-removebg.png?raw=true"
                    alt="NakamaStream Logo" 
                    class="w-32 h-32 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 mx-auto animate-float" />
                <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-custom-red text-center mt-6">NakamaStream</h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Mensaje Principal -->
            <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 text-center px-4 sm:px-0">
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-custom-red to-red-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                    ¡Sitio en Mantenimiento!
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Estamos realizando mejoras en NakamaStream para brindarte una mejor experiencia.
                    Volveremos pronto con grandes novedades.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Barra de Progreso -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-0">
                <div class="h-2 w-full bg-gray-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-custom-red to-red-400 w-full animate-pulse-slow"></div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-center mt-4">Mantenimiento en curso...</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Enlaces -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 mt-8 sm:mt-12 px-4 sm:px-0">
                <a href="https://discord.gg/nakamastream"
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 bg-custom-red hover:bg-red-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
                    <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center">
                        <i class="fab fa-discord text-xl sm:text-2xl mr-2 sm:mr-3"></i>
                        <span class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold">Unirse al Discord</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
                
                <a href="/releases"
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 bg-[#121212] hover:bg-custom-red rounded-full border border-custom-red transition-all duration-300">
                    <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-history text-xl sm:text-2xl mr-2 sm:mr-3"></i>
                        <span class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold">Historial de Releases</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
